@startuml
title Dify 通过 MCP + Socket.IO 触发客户端界面的时序图

actor User as 用户
participant Browser as 浏览器前端
participant ChatAPI as "/chat/create\n/chat/completion"
database Redis as Redis
participant Dify as "Dify/Agent"
participant MCP as "/mcp/smart-tools"
participant SocketServer as SocketServer

== 建立本地会话与Socket连接 ==
用户 -> 浏览器前端 : 打开 Demo 页面并发起聊天
浏览器前端 -> ChatAPI : POST /chat/create
ChatAPI -> Redis : save_session(session_id,...)
Redis --> ChatAPI : ok
ChatAPI --> 浏览器前端 : 返回 session_id
浏览器前端 -> SocketServer : connect(auth.sessionId=session_id)
SocketServer -> SocketServer : enter_room(sid, session_id)
SocketServer --> 浏览器前端 : 连接成功

== 发起 Dify 对话 ==
用户 -> 浏览器前端 : 输入问题
浏览器前端 -> ChatAPI : POST /chat/completion(session_id,...)
ChatAPI -> Redis : get_session(session_id)
Redis --> ChatAPI : session payload
ChatAPI -> ChatAPI : 注入 inputs.__session_id__
ChatAPI -> Dify : create_chat_message(..., inputs.__session_id__)
alt 首次会话未绑定 conversation_id
  Dify --> ChatAPI : 返回 answer + conversation_id
  ChatAPI -> Redis : set_conversation_id(session_id, conversation_id)
else 已存在 conversation_id
  Dify --> ChatAPI : 返回 answer
end
ChatAPI --> 浏览器前端 : SSE/JSON 聊天结果

== Dify 调用 MCP Tool 触发客户端界面 ==
Dify -> MCP : 调用 Tool(session_id)
MCP -> MCP : 组装 payload\n{type:function,name,params}
MCP -> SocketServer : emit_session_event(session_id, payload)
SocketServer -> SocketServer : emit("message", payload, to=session_id)
SocketServer --> 浏览器前端 : message(payload)
浏览器前端 -> 浏览器前端 : handleSocketMessage()
浏览器前端 -> 浏览器前端 : socketFunctionHandlers[name]()
浏览器前端 -> 浏览器前端 : 打开对应弹窗/界面
MCP --> Dify : 返回 success + payload

@enduml
